mes New Roman" w:cs="Times New Roman"/><w:b/><w:bCs/></w:rPr><w:t>Library</w:t></w:r></w:p><w:p w14:paraId="74799FC8" w14:textId="600BE32E" w:rsidR="00576960" w:rsidRPr="00576960" w:rsidRDefault="00576960" w:rsidP="00576960"><w:pPr><w:rPr><w:rFonts w:ascii="Times New Roman" w:hAnsi="Times New Roman" w:cs="Times New Roman"/></w:rPr></w:pPr><w:r w:rsidRPr="00576960"><w:rPr><w:rFonts w:ascii="Times New Roman" w:hAnsi="Times New Roman" w:cs="Times New Roman"/></w:rPr><w:t xml:space="preserve">Information is at the heart of meaningful learning in schools. To promote a spirit of continuous learning amongst students, </w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="001209D5" w:rsidRPr="001209D5"><w:rPr><w:rFonts w:ascii="Times New Roman" w:hAnsi="Times New Roman" w:cs="Times New Roman"/></w:rPr><w:t>Vasundhara</w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidRPr="00576960"><w:rPr><w:rFonts w:ascii="Times New Roman" w:hAnsi="Times New Roman" w:cs="Times New Roman"/></w:rPr><w:t xml:space="preserve"> assures peaceful and enriching hours in the library. Students are encouraged to cultivate good reading habits and use the library as an important </w:t></w:r><w:proofErr w:type="spellStart"/><w:r w:rsidRPr="00576960"><w:rPr><w:rFonts w:ascii="Times New Roman" w:hAnsi="Times New Roman" w:cs="Times New Roman"/></w:rPr><w:t>centre</w:t></w:r><w:proofErr w:type="spellEnd"/><w:r w:rsidRPr="00576960"><w:rPr><w:rFonts w:ascii="Times New Roman" w:hAnsi="Times New Roman" w:cs="Times New Roman"/></w:rPr><w:t xml:space="preserve"> for learning. Books, journals and magazines from across the world are made available to the students. Each student can choose his own corner and explore history, literature or science. Undisturbed. Personal supervision is provided to every child to improve his reading and speaking abilities. The library has separate reading halls for primary and secondary sections. Few notable features of our library are:</w:t></w:r></w:p><w:p w14:paraId="78F3AC6C" w14:textId="77777777" w:rsidR="00576960" w:rsidRPr="00576960" w:rsidRDefault="00576960" w:rsidP="00576960"><w:pPr><w:numPr><w:ilvl w:val="0"/><w:numId w:val="3"/></w:numPr><w:rPr><w:rFonts w:ascii="Times New Roman" w:hAnsi="Times New Roman" w:cs="Times New Roman"/></w:rPr></w:pPr><w:r w:rsidRPr="00576960"><w:rPr><w:rFonts w:ascii="Times New Roman" w:hAnsi="Times New Roman" w:cs="Times New Roman"/></w:rPr><w:t>Well stocked libraries for pre-primary, primary and secondary sections.</w:t></w:r></w:p><w:p w14:paraId="372A9350" w14:textId="77777777" w:rsidR="00576960" w:rsidRPr="00576960" w:rsidRDefault="00576960" w:rsidP="00576960"><w:pPr><w:numPr><w:ilvl w:val="0"/><w:numId w:val="3"/></w:numPr><w:rPr><w:rFonts w:ascii="Times New Roman" w:hAnsi="Times New Roman" w:cs="Times New Roman"/></w:rPr></w:pPr><w:proofErr w:type="spellStart"/><w:r w:rsidRPr="00576960"><w:rPr><w:rFonts w:ascii="Times New Roman" w:hAnsi="Times New Roman" w:cs="Times New Roman"/></w:rPr><w:t>Computerised</w:t></w:r><w:proofErr w:type="spellEnd"/><w:r w:rsidRPr="00576960"><w:rPr><w:rFonts w:ascii="Times New Roman" w:hAnsi="Times New Roman" w:cs="Times New Roman"/></w:rPr><w:t xml:space="preserve"> system to keep libraries up to date.</w:t></w:r></w:p><w:p w14:paraId="77622313" w14:textId="77777777" w:rsidR="00576960" w:rsidRPr="00576960" w:rsidRDefault="00576960" w:rsidP="00576960"><w:pPr><w:numPr><w:ilvl w:val="0"/><w:numId w:val="3"/></w:numPr><w:rPr><w:rFonts w:ascii="Times New Roman" w:hAnsi="Times New Roman" w:cs="Times New Roman"/></w:rPr></w:pPr><w:r w:rsidRPr="00576960"><w:rPr><w:rFonts w:ascii="Times New Roman" w:hAnsi="Times New Roman" w:cs="Times New Roman"/></w:rPr><w:t>An abundance of reference material including multimedia equipment</w:t></w:r></w:p><w:p w14:paraId="0AE886E4" w14:textId="77777777" w:rsidR="00576960" w:rsidRPr="00576960" w:rsidRDefault="00576960" w:rsidP="00576960"><w:pPr><w:numPr><w:ilvl w:val="0"/><w:numId w:val="3"/></w:numPr><w:rPr><w:rFonts w:ascii="Times New Roman" w:hAnsi="Times New Roman" w:cs="Times New Roman"/></w:rPr></w:pPr><w:r w:rsidRPr="00576960"><w:rPr><w:rFonts w:ascii="Times New Roman" w:hAnsi="Times New Roman" w:cs="Times New Roman"/></w:rPr><w:t>Newspapers, magazines, periodicals to keep students &amp; staff well informed</w:t></w:r></w:p><w:p w14:paraId="158B9D64" w14:textId="77777777" w:rsidR="00576960" w:rsidRPr="00576960" w:rsidRDefault="00576960" w:rsidP="00576960"><w:pPr><w:numPr><w:ilvl w:val="0"/><w:numId w:val="3"/></w:numPr><w:rPr><w:rFonts w:ascii="Times New Roman" w:hAnsi="Times New Roman" w:cs="Times New Roman"/></w:rPr></w:pPr><w:r w:rsidRPr="00576960"><w:rPr><w:rFonts w:ascii="Times New Roman" w:hAnsi="Times New Roman" w:cs="Times New Roman"/></w:rPr><w:t>Reading / story telling sessions with the aid of puppets.</w:t></w:r></w:p><w:p w14:paraId="23990F70" w14:textId="77777777" w:rsidR="00E83150" w:rsidRPr="001209D5" w:rsidRDefault="00E83150"><w:pPr><w:rPr><w:rFonts w:ascii="Times New Roman" w:hAnsi="Times New Roman" w:cs="Times New Roman"/></w:rPr></w:pPr></w:p><w:sectPr w:rsidR="00E83150" w:rsidRPr="001209D5" w:rsidSect="00F468D8"><w:pgSz w:w="11906" w:h="16838" w:code="9"/><w:pgMar w:top="720" w:right="720" w:bottom="720" w:left="720" w:header="720" w:footer="720" w:gutter="0"/><w:cols w:space="720"/><w:docGrid w:linePitch="360"/></w:sectPr></w:body></w:document>